{"name":"Lemon Prawn Risotto ","slug":"lemon-prawn-risotto","description":"<p>Join our risotto revolution! Say goodbye to endless stirring and stovetop chaos because today, we're making a creamy and dreamy risotto right in the microwave. In just a few simple steps, you'll be wondering why you ever bothered with the stovetop.&nbsp;</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"Lemon Orzo Chicken Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Vegetable Broth","quantity":"4 cups prepared","additionalInstruction":"warmed"},{"name":"Vegetable Broth Mix","quantity":"1 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"boiling water","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"arborio rice ","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"uncooked, frozen peeled prawns","quantity":"<sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> lb (340 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"frozen peas","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"sour cream","quantity":"<sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"25 min","servings":"6 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Place seasoning, broth, rice, and butter in <a data-item-id=\"38e9c45d-465e-4a8b-8c16-5f437f361347\" href=\"\">Round</a> or <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>; stir to combine. Cover; microwave on high 8 min.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Remove from microwave; stir in prawns. Cover; microwave on high for 8 min.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Remove from microwave; stir in peas. Cover; microwave on high 6 min.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Fold in sour cream. Top with Parmesan, if desired. Serve warm; risotto will continue to thicken as it cools.&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"steamers","name":"Steamers"},{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"fish___seafood","name":"Fish & Seafood"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"easter","name":"Easter"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"},{"slug":"valentine_s_day","name":"Valentine’s Day"},{"slug":"microwave","name":"Microwave"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"mother_s_day","name":"Mother’s Day"},{"slug":"gluten_free_e8446d0","name":"Gluten-free"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"garlic_free","name":"Garlic-free"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":400,"fat":8,"saturatedFat":5,"transFat":0.2,"cholesterol":110,"sodium":240,"carbohydrate":60,"fiber":4,"sugars":4,"protein":20},"tips":"<p>Enjoy risotto hot and fresh—the rice will continue to absorb liquid as it cools so it’s best to serve it&nbsp;immediately.</p>"}